Project #:  28 





 











ZotVerse 



Project #:  28 




Members:Gurkanwal Singh Kang, Anish Pandita, Mayank Chandak, Neelendu Wadhwa






Description:Our platform “ZotVerse” helps UCI members who want to buy and sell refurbished items to verified UCI members. With facilities like real-time auctions and a college-oriented dashboard feed, we aim to bridge the gap between potential buyers and sellers. Our price bidding functionality enables no price disparity and secure payments powered by PayPal payment gateway ensuring safe and easy transactions. Join us to get a seamless E-commerce experience and also promote the reusability of used products.






